    <releaseNotes><![CDATA[
Release notes are available in our blog https://www.hangfire.io/blog/
Please see https://docs.hangfire.io/en/latest/upgrade-guides/upgrading-to-hangfire-1.8.html to learn how to upgrade.

1.8.24
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Russian translation for Dashboard UI (by @akortunov).
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Slow log can now detect blocked extension filter executions.

1.8.23
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Use stable sorting algorithm for background job filters again (by @jirikanda).
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Add missing keys for Swedish translation (by @karl-sjogren).
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Custom `AutomaticRetryAttribute` is ignored under certain conditions (by @jirikanda).
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Use `TypeNameAssemblyFormatHandling` in tests with .NET 6 (by @viktor-vintertass).

1.8.22
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `IGlobalConfiguration.UseNoOpLogProvider` method to disable logging.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Un-deprecate interval methods in the `Cron` class, add remarks in docs instead.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Bump internalized version of Cronos to 0.11.1.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Bump internalized version of Microsoft.Owin to 4.2.3.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Serialization of arrays of nested types `SimpleAssemblyTypeSerializer`.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Remove wrong escaping characters in Portuguese translations on the "Servers" page.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Properly remove registered `IBackgroundProcessingServer` instances on OWIN app shutdown.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď `AspNetShutdownDetector` for early ASP.NET shutdown detection is not working (regression from 1.7.30).
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Replace the `netcoreapp3.1` target with the `net8.0` one in tests.

1.8.21
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `FailedState.IncludeFileInfo` to optionally show/hide line numbers in exceptions in Failed state.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Include line numbers for exceptions by default when available.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Portuguese (Brazil) translations in Strings.pt-BR.resx (by @pedro-cons).
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Static `BackgroundJob` class always acquires the most current `JobStorage.Current` instance.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Static `RecurringJob` class always acquires the most current `JobStorage.Current` instance.

1.8.20
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Glyphicons from Bootstrap are not displaying after upgrading to version 1.8.19.

1.8.19
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Update Bootstrap to the custom version of 3.4.2 to avoid false alerts on unused features.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Typos in Portuguese translation (by @VianaArthur).
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Unnecessary recurring job update transaction when nothing is changed after an error.

1.8.18
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `DashboardOptions.ServerPossiblyAbortedThreshold` to configure a custom threshold for "possibly aborted" warnings.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Expired jobs are still shown on the "Retries" page in some cases.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Issues with `CultureInfo`-related differences after upgrading to 1.8.15‚Äď1.8.17.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Don't leak `AsyncLocal` values from synchronous background job methods.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Don't throw an exception when passing the `Job.Args` property to the `Job` class' constructor.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Make the lock file usable for both .NET 8.0 and .NET 9.0 builds.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Make code generation for `cshtml` files working on newer platforms.

1.8.16
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Include fewer stack frames in exceptions come from `IServerFilter` implementations.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Don't include file information in the `ExceptionDetails` property of a FailedState instance.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Switch back to `CancellationEvent` usage instead of `CancellationToken.WaitHandle`.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Don't commit external transaction in the `BackgroundJobStateChanger` implementation.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Use safe default serializer settings for Newtonsoft.Json 12.X and below.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Fix builds for the `net451` platform when using .NET 9.0.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Significantly reduce execution time of unit tests in the `RecurringJobSchedulerFacts` class.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Bump `Microsoft.CodeAnalysis.NetAnalyzers` package to version 9.0.0.

1.8.15
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď New `AutomaticRetryAttribute.ExceptOn` property to skip retries for specific exceptions.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Refactor filters pipeline to use less LINQ magic and fewer allocations.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Use `GetCultureInfo` instead of creating an instance in the `CaptureCultureAttribute` filter.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Cache some immutable data to avoid extra allocations.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Improve loopback address detection (by @meziantou).
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Reformulate misleading error messages regarding retry timings (by @RGFuaWVs).
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Problem with missing localizations in the previous version.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Don't hide exception details on Failed Jobs page when the exception message is empty.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Problems with the first restore when using the `build.bat` command.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Better display of canceled recurring jobs in dashboard.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Less overall allocations with using static delegates and struct-based iterators.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Improve precision of some diagnostic messages in the wait protection logic.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Make all private and internal classes sealed to improve code consistency.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Less overall pressure on garbage collector.

1.8.13 and 1.8.14
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Partial cache for serialization and deserialization in `InvocationData` to produce less strings.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Add caching for default type serializer and resolver.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Don't let `JobFilter`-related logic to show up in profilers.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Modify `IProfiler` to be less allocatey for diagnostic purposes that almost never run.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Prefer using `CancellationToken.WaitHandle` again, since early .NET Core days are gone.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Fewer allocations when working with `IStateHandler` collections in a state machine.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Redirect the "System.Private.Xml.Linq" assembly to the "System.Xml.Linq" one for better interoperability.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Don't throw `KeyNotFoundException` when recurring job is malformed.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Proper relative path calculation in `UrlHelper.To` for OWIN-based Dashboard UI (by @LordJZ).
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Typo in the Turkish localization file (by @ismkdc).
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Switch to a modern PowerShell 7+ to speed up SignPath installation on AppVeyor.

1.8.12
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `MaxDegreeOfParallelismForSchedulers` experimental server option if supported by storage.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Experimental support for parallel execution of the delayed job scheduler.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Experimental support for parallel execution of the recurring job scheduler.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Recurring job is scheduled to the past after recovering from error with `AddOrUpdate`.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď `AddOrUpdate` triggers execution of a recurring job, even if its next execution is in the future.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Two very minor errors in the Swedish localization file (by @Uglack).

1.8.11
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Add icons and fix metadata for NuGet packages.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Bump ILRepack to version 2.0.27 to avoid problems with internalizing.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď "Type exists in both Cronos and Hangfire.Core" exception.

1.8.10
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Added Norwegian translations for new keys (by @khellang).
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Update Brazilian Portuguese translation (by @HugoAlames).
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Bump Cronos dependency to version 0.8.3.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Enable NuGet package and DLL signing with a company certificate.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Require NuGet package signature validation on restore for dependencies.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Add `HangfireIO` as a package owner.

1.8.9
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Use `Environment.MachineName` as a server name if other environment vars aren't available.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Bump the Cronos package version from 0.7.1 to 0.8.1.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Improve portuguese translations (by @filipe-silva).
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Possible `NullReferenceException` on the Deleted Jobs page (regression from 1.8.7).
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Enable full source link support with embedded symbols and repository-based sources.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Enable repeatable package restore using a lock file.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Run unit tests against the `net6.0` platform.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Modernise the build system and clean up the build scripts.

1.8.7
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Allow using macro expressions like `@hourly` for recurring jobs (by @MuhamedAbdalla).
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Show storage time in page footer when supported by storage implementation.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Show duration and latency columns separately on the Succeeded Jobs page when supported.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Show the exception column on the Deleted Jobs page when available and supported by storage.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Reduce package size by stripping unnecessary locales in Moment.js.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Bump Microsoft.Owin package to version 4.2.2.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Log a warning message when a server listens to unsupported queue names.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Use storage time, if available, to show delay warnings in the Dashboard UI.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Proper rendering of generic arguments on the Job Details page (by @olivermue).
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Language inconsistency in the Dashboard UI related to date/time description.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Big stack traces take too long time to be formatted.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Don't throw `NullReferenceException` from the Scheduled Jobs page when there's a job with missing data.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Don't throw `NullReferenceException` from the Processing Jobs page when there's a job with missing data.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď CSS for Enqueued and Deleted state cards in dark theme.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Log errors instead of throwing an exception when a particular table can't be cleaned.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Avoid logging fatal exceptions when stopping a faulting background process.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Don't display checkboxes in the Dashboard UI when job details can not be fetched.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Scrollbars in WebKit-based browsers are now dark in dark mode.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Disable tests for `netcoreapp1.0` and `netcoreapp2.1` targets since they aren't supported in AppVeyor.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Add a `net6.0` target for unit tests instead of the removed ones.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Modernise projects and build environments to use the newest features.

1.8.6
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Update jQuery library in Dashboard UI to version 3.7.1.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Mark all types in Hangfire.Annotations with `EditorBrowsableAttribute(Never)`.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Change state card colors for the Awaiting state to match the Scheduled state.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Exception when deserializing an instance of the `AutomaticRetryAttribute` class from JSON.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Add serialization-related constructors for all the exception classes.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Use invariant culture or ordinal comparisons for internal strings.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Use invariant culture when formatting key names for metrics.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Use `CurrentCulture` instead of `CurrentUICulture` when displaying time.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Enable running static analysis by Coverity Scan weekly.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Enable mandatory static analysis by the Microsoft.CodeAnalysis.NetAnalyzers package.
‚ÄĘ Project ‚Äď Change MSBuild path when building using newer .NET SDKs for Razor views.

1.8.5
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Possibility to inform a `FaviconPath` on `DashboardOptions` (by @cezar-pimentel).
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Inability to restore a disabled recurring job, regression in version 1.8.3.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Make it possible to serialize the `AutomaticRetryAttribute` filter to JSON.

1.8.4
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Pass server id from a worker to the `PerformContext.ServerId` property available in filters.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Send heartbeats until full background processing server shutdown.

1.8.3
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Allow to configure `MaxLinesInStackTrace` for a particular `FailedState` instance.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Remove job id from schedule when it's not in the Scheduled state for some reason.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Missing invocations of recurring jobs when the new "Ignorable" option is used.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Make `DisableConcurrentExecutionAttribute` and `LatencyTimeoutAttribute` serializable.

1.8.2
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Disable transactional job creation feature appeared in 1.8.0.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď "Can not start continuation XXX" error when storage supports transactional job creation.

1.8.1
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `MisfireHandlingMode.Ignorable` to avoid scheduling recurring jobs on missed schedules.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Support disabling dark mode via the `DashboardOptions.DarkModeEnabled` property.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Remove the 1-hour limitation for the `WithJobExpirationTimeout` configuration method.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Add missing `UseDefaultCulture` configuration method overloads.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Add missing `UseDashboardStylesheet` and `UseJobDetailsRenderer` configuration methods.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Give even more space for identifiers on the Recurring Jobs page.
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď `state-card-state-active` color is not very dark (by @coolhome).
‚ÄĘ Fixed ‚Äď Slightly change chart proportions to fit 4K in Dashboard UI.

1.8.0
‚ÄĘ Breaking ‚Äď Dropped the `NET45` platform target in favor of the `NET451` target to support Visual Studio 2022.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Introduce the `Job.Queue` property, so jobs now can have their own queue specified.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Method overloads to create background jobs directly with a custom default queue.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Method overloads to create recurring jobs directly with a custom default queue.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `IBackgroundJobClient.Create` method overloads with the new `queue` parameter.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Allow to filter exception types in `AutomaticRetryAttribute` by using the new `OnlyOn` property.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `DeletedState` now has the persisted `Exception` property populated after a failure.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `JobContinuationOptions.OnlyOnDeletedState` to create continuations after a failure.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `Exception` job parameter is passed to continuation when `UseResultsInContinuations` method is used.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `FromExceptionAttribute` to deal with an antecedent exception in a background job continuation.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Make it possible to specify multiple `JobContinuationOptions` values for a continuation.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `BackgroundJobServerOptions.IsLightweightServer` option to run a server with no storage processes.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Ability to use custom formattable resource identifiers for the `DisableConcurrentExecution` filter.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Pass `ServerId` to `FailedState` instances to simplify the debugging on different servers.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Allow to pass job parameters when creating a job (by @brian-knoll-micronetonline).
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `MisfireHandlingMode.Strict` to create a job for each missed recurring job occurrence.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Support for default culture and UI culture via the `UseDefaultCulture` configuration method.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Introduce the `captureDefault` parameter in the `CaptureCulture` filter.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `IGlobalConfiguration.UseFilterProvider` extension method to unify the configuration.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Built-in `Remove` method for `JobFilterCollection` to remove global filters based on their type.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `CompatibilityLevel.Version_180` flag to avoid storing culture parameters when they are the same as the default ones.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Create job atomically when `Transaction.CreateJob` feature is supported by the storage.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Query time from storage in recurring and delayed schedulers when supported by storage.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Move job to the `DeletedState` instead of `SucceededState` when its invocation was canceled by a filter.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Speedup delayed jobs when a custom default queue is specified by avoiding extra state transition.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Use UI culture from `CurrentCulture` parameter when `CurrentUICulture` one is missing.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Increase the default value for the `BackgroundJobServerOptions.StopTimeout` to 500 ms.
‚ÄĘ Deprecated ‚Äď `AddOrUpdate` overloads with optional params defined in the `RecurringJobManagerExtensions` class.
‚ÄĘ Deprecated ‚Äď `AddOrUpdate` overloads with optional parameters defined in the `RecurringJob` class.
‚ÄĘ Deprecated ‚Äď `AddOrUpdate` method overloads with no `recurringJobId` parameter.
‚ÄĘ Deprecated ‚Äď `RecurringJobOptions.QueueName` property, new methods should be used instead.
‚ÄĘ Breaking ‚Äď Dropped `NET45` platform target in favor of `NET451` target to support Visual Studio 2022.

Dashboard UI
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Dark mode support for Dashboard UI depending on the system settings (by @danillewin).
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Dashboard UI now has a full-width layout to display more data (by @danillewin).
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Allow to add custom JavaScript and CSS files to the Dashboard UI via the `DashboardRoutes` class.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `DefaultRecordsPerPage` property on the `DashboardOptions` class (by @PaulARoy).
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `IGlobalConfiguration.UseJobDetailsRenderer` method for custom renderers for the Job Details page.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Display deleted jobs in the Realtime and History graphs when supported by storage.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `IGlobalConfiguration.UseDashboardMetrics` extension method to pass multiple metrics at once.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď State renderer for the `DeletedState` to display its new exception property.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Support for new `MonitoringApi` methods for the Awaiting Jobs page.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Make it possible to display methods of non-loaded jobs in the Dashboard UI when supported by storage.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Improved display of realtime chart with more accents on failed and deleted jobs.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Don't display the queue name in the state transition list when it's the `default` one.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Display scheduled job count when the enqueued count is zero on the main metric.

Extensibility
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `Factory`, `StateMachine`, and `Performer` properties to context classes to avoid injecting services.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Allow to pass custom data to `ApplyStateContext` and `ElectStateContext` instances.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Preserve custom data dictionary between the entire filter chain.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Allow to pass a transaction to background job state changer when new methods are implemented.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Ignore some members when serializing a `JobFilterAttribute` instance to decrease the payload size.

Storage
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Virtual `JobStorage.GetReadOnlyConnection` method intended to return `JobStorageConnection` for replicas.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Virtual `JobStorage.HasFeature` method for querying optional features.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď The `JobStorageFeatures` class to avoid using magic strings in storage features.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Optional `GetSetCount`, `GetSetContains`, and `GetUtcDateTime` methods for the `JobStorageConnection` class.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Optional `AcquireDistributedLock` and `RemoveFromQueue` methods for the `JobStorageTransaction` class.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Optional `CreateJob` and `SetJobParameter` methods for the `JobStorageTransaction` class.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Optional `ParametersSnapshot` property for `BackgroundJob` and `JobData` classes to minimize roundtrips in the future.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Support for transactional acknowledgment using a new storage method for better handling some data loss scenarios.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď Fetch `Retries` and `Awaiting` metrics in `StatisticsDto` properties when supported by storage.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď The `JobStorageMonitor` class with more available methods for the new features.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Allow to query job parameters without additional roundtrip when supported by storage.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Expose state data dictionaries in list DTOs when supported by storage.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Rely on storage indexing with the `Monitoring.AwaitingJobs` feature.

Internals
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `IBackgroundProcess.UseBackgroundPool` now allows to pass thread configuration logic.
‚ÄĘ Added ‚Äď `BackgroundJobServerOptions.WorkerThreadConfigurationAction` option for custom thread configuration.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Allow changing queues on the fly with custom worker configuration.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Avoid storage roundtrip to query job data in worker, take data from previous state change.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď `FromParameterAttribute`-based logic now always overwrites arguments, even with non-null values.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Turn the `JobContinuationOptions` enum into flags while still possible.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď Re-implement `TaskExtensions.WaitOneAsync` only with the `RegisterWaitForSingleObject` method.
‚ÄĘ Changed ‚Äď `ServerHeartbeatProcess` now uses `ThreadPriority.AboveNormal` to prioritize heartbeats.
]]>
    </releaseNotes>
